Read Colossians chapter two.

41:07.121 --> 41:09.224
So you're shifting from the faith.

41:09.244 --> 41:10.546
Where are you going, Galatians?

41:10.566 --> 41:11.387
Who has bewitched you?

41:11.427 --> 41:12.188
What are you doing?

41:12.208 --> 41:14.451
You thought that you're going to be perfected in the flesh.

41:14.491 --> 41:17.194
You were justified by Christ and his blood.

41:17.215 --> 41:20.359
And now you're going to be made perfect by your righteousness and your law keeping.

41:20.379 --> 41:21.981
Paul is just constantly blowing whistles.

41:22.021 --> 41:23.663
Hey, hey, no, stop foul.

